WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: rG85RDmWo8s

NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.530 --> 00:00:09.800
Yesterday I told you about the Void, the dharma,
which one has to establish.

00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:18.330
In modern times, people have used their freedom
to such an extent, you see, they have moved

00:00:18.330 --> 00:00:21.500
so much to this extreme or to that extreme.

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:30.450
They have left their central path and have
accepted and identified themselves with such

00:00:30.450 --> 00:00:40.920
an extreme ideas about everything, that it
is rather difficult to convince people that

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:43.890
they have lost their way.

00:00:43.890 --> 00:00:47.559
All extremes are wrong.

00:00:47.559 --> 00:00:53.210
Moderation is the way we really solve the
problem.

00:00:53.210 --> 00:00:57.789
But human race is such that everybody starts
running very fast, you see, and there’s

00:00:57.789 --> 00:00:59.699
a competition set in: who goes first to hell.

00:00:59.699 --> 00:01:03.329
[Laughter, She laughs]

00:01:03.329 --> 00:01:11.909
It’s not only in one direction, you can
take up any direction, but all these directions

00:01:11.909 --> 00:01:19.120
are linear.

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:30.780
They move straightforward and coil back and
go down – any movement of that kind.

00:01:30.780 --> 00:01:37.420
For example take our, say, industrial development.

00:01:37.420 --> 00:01:44.000
We started our industrial development without
understanding the whole, the world as a whole,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:51.210
that the whole world was created by God, not
a part, one country.

00:01:51.210 --> 00:01:55.560
Without understanding the relationship with
the whole, when we start moving industrially,

00:01:55.560 --> 00:02:00.329
we created industries, and to pamper them
we had to create other industries.

00:02:00.329 --> 00:02:11.460
Then also to keep the hungry machines working
out, we had to feed them with something.

00:02:11.460 --> 00:02:22.670
And thus we created a horrible system of extracting
things from the Mother Earth, using them.

00:02:22.670 --> 00:02:29.040
We have so many things, but we do not have
the thing which is your Spirit.

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:37.780
We never thought that, after all, all this
matter is for what?

00:02:37.780 --> 00:02:39.019
All these things are for what?

00:02:39.019 --> 00:02:40.019
For comfort?

00:02:40.019 --> 00:02:46.780
That also, if not done in moderation, we are
going to be ruined, completely ruined.

00:02:46.780 --> 00:02:54.540
We’ll become like worms.

00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:59.590
The Mother Earth is available to you, that
doesn’t mean that you should be indiscriminate

00:02:59.590 --> 00:03:01.819
and use it for your comfort.

00:03:01.819 --> 00:03:07.780
She’s there for your comfort, no doubt,
She’s the comforting element we have got,

00:03:07.780 --> 00:03:09.599
the greatest comforting element.

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:14.659
But we do not know how to use Her for our
comfort.

00:03:14.659 --> 00:03:23.680
The way we use Her is by taking out, extracting
Her.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:27.820
Now if I say that, the other extreme would
be: “We’ll have no possessions, nothing,

00:03:27.820 --> 00:03:30.390
live, hang by the string, some shoestring
somewhere”.

00:03:30.390 --> 00:03:36.910
[She laughs] There are people who believe
in such a thing also, who want to live on

00:03:36.910 --> 00:03:49.739
a shoestring and have all kinds of diseases,
physical, mental, because they are living

00:03:49.739 --> 00:03:55.450
abnormally, in such a way that they do not
relate themselves to the Mother Earth at all.

00:03:55.450 --> 00:04:03.100
Either you abstract completely whatever She
has, or take away all Her flesh, blood, everything,

00:04:03.100 --> 00:04:07.040
and otherwise you have nothing to do.

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:09.800
These are two extremes!

00:04:09.800 --> 00:04:18.889
And once you start doing like that, you find
that you become slave to both ways, because

00:04:18.889 --> 00:04:25.130
you start forming habits with the help of
this matter.

00:04:25.130 --> 00:04:31.200
Habit formation is slavery, complete slavery,
even a habit formation like fasting.

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:33.090
Now some people have to fast.

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:36.160
Who has asked them to fast I don’t know.

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:40.000
What is the need to fast for people who are
already suffering from liver troubles and

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.280
thin like sticks?

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:48.139
It’s all right, somebody has to fast because,
supposing he has too much weight, or say they

00:04:48.139 --> 00:04:50.610
want some rest to the stomach, is all right.

00:04:50.610 --> 00:04:57.710
But this fasting also can become such a habit,
such a habit, that the day you do not fast

00:04:57.710 --> 00:04:58.740
you’ll say, “Oh!

00:04:58.740 --> 00:05:01.180
You have done the greatest crime on the Earth.

00:05:01.180 --> 00:05:05.130
Oh God, I did not fast on Thursday, I should
have fasted."

00:05:05.130 --> 00:05:07.360
In India we get so many mad people like that.

00:05:07.360 --> 00:05:10.669
[Laughter] They go crazy because they have
not fasted.

00:05:10.669 --> 00:05:14.930
There are some who get crazy because they
have not eaten their food.

00:05:14.930 --> 00:05:18.590
I mean they are all right, but if they have
not taken their lunch, for them it’s the

00:05:18.590 --> 00:05:26.930
greatest injury, the greatest injustice done
to them that they have not been able to take

00:05:26.930 --> 00:05:28.950
their lunch.

00:05:28.950 --> 00:05:38.940
The matter starts enslaving you and your mind
becomes a slave of that matter.

00:05:38.940 --> 00:05:46.160
You do not know in what way this Mother Earth,
which is there to give you the ultimate, She’s

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:51.720
the one who resides within you at the Mooladhara
Chakra to give you the innocence.

00:05:51.720 --> 00:05:54.770
She gives you the innocence.

00:05:54.770 --> 00:06:02.830
Instead of taking that essence of Hers, the
innocence, what you take is the matter which

00:06:02.830 --> 00:06:03.830
is dead.

00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:09.460
The living principle of Mother Earth is innocence,
Her magnetism, Her gravity.

00:06:09.460 --> 00:06:19.930
Instead of that, what do you take out of Her
is this matter.

00:06:19.930 --> 00:06:24.319
Either you run away from it, or you run towards
it.

00:06:24.319 --> 00:06:26.430
Nothing in between.

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:35.090
Now matter is there for you to use, no doubt;
but to use so that you do not get dominated

00:06:35.090 --> 00:06:39.710
by it, because you are the supreme thing God
has created.

00:06:39.710 --> 00:06:44.169
You are the supreme-most thing; all the elements
are working in you.

00:06:44.169 --> 00:06:50.979
There’s no animal in the world who has all
these elements working in such a beautiful

00:06:50.979 --> 00:07:00.340
fashion that you develop your own will, your
own freedom.

00:07:00.340 --> 00:07:08.120
It’s such a intricate process which has
worked out a human being, which we don’t

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:15.250
realize, where you develop your own will,
your own freedom.

00:07:15.250 --> 00:07:24.460
But again, with your own will what do you
do is to lose your freedom all the time.

00:07:24.460 --> 00:07:28.960
For example, take a person who indulges in
luxuries.

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:35.919
I mean he is idiotic sometimes, I mean he
really becomes an idiot the way he goes on.

00:07:35.919 --> 00:07:38.440
I mean you can see that he’s an idiot and
stupid fellow.

00:07:38.440 --> 00:07:41.979
The another one, he will say that this luxury
is – indulgence fellow is very, very idiotic

00:07:41.979 --> 00:07:42.979
and stupid you can see.

00:07:42.979 --> 00:07:44.229
So he says, “All right, let me give it up."

00:07:44.229 --> 00:07:49.789
He goes to another extreme, to such an extreme
that he becomes a dry person, absolutely dry.

00:07:49.789 --> 00:07:54.910
The innocence is in the centre.

00:07:54.910 --> 00:08:01.090
For example, the best use of the Mother Earth
is to watch Her working.

00:08:01.090 --> 00:08:03.259
Watch the nature.

00:08:03.259 --> 00:08:06.319
Watch every tree, what beautiful personality
every tree has.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:09.810
Every leaf of the tree stands against the
sky.

00:08:09.810 --> 00:08:15.879
I mean it’s such a poetry to feel Her with
your feet.

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:19.169
How soft She is when She produces flowers
for you.

00:08:19.169 --> 00:08:23.000
You have to learn so much from what She does.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:29.879
She creates a flower to emit fragrance, to
give, to give, to give.

00:08:29.879 --> 00:08:33.710
She just gives.

00:08:33.710 --> 00:08:39.450
Her innocence doesn’t bother as to what
you are, whether you deserve it or not, whether

00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:43.990
you are a good person or a bad person or what
use you are going to put Her resources, She

00:08:43.990 --> 00:08:45.910
just gives.

00:08:45.910 --> 00:08:51.820
She doesn’t judge you.

00:08:51.820 --> 00:08:56.250
Nirvaj – it flows.

00:08:56.250 --> 00:08:58.740
The capital flows without any interest.

00:08:58.740 --> 00:09:07.190
It just goes on flowing and flowing and that’s
the word of nirvaj is.

00:09:07.190 --> 00:09:15.010
It doesn’t think to whom She is giving to,
whether they deserve it or not, if they are

00:09:15.010 --> 00:09:17.840
sinners or they are this or that.

00:09:17.840 --> 00:09:22.440
But now it is for you to use your wisdom.

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:31.140
And She has created this deity [Ganesha] of
wisdom within you, and you have to keep that

00:09:31.140 --> 00:09:32.350
deity awakened.

00:09:32.350 --> 00:09:37.480
He came, incarnated on this Earth as Jesus
Christ.

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:40.340
Look at Him.

00:09:40.340 --> 00:09:44.140
Look at His life.

00:09:44.140 --> 00:09:46.990
How He lived.

00:09:46.990 --> 00:09:57.440
He was a carpenter’s son; He lived like
a carpenter’s son.

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:01.240
He didn’t amass money.

00:10:01.240 --> 00:10:04.250
And what a dynamic life in thirty years of
His age!

00:10:04.250 --> 00:10:09.480
What a dynamic life, out of which He spent
only four years in the public.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:15.830
With all our indulgences and with all our
comforts, with all our movements and aeroplanes

00:10:15.830 --> 00:10:21.640
and all this, how many there are who have
created such a dynamic life?

00:10:21.640 --> 00:10:29.260
What dynamism have we been able to show, the
dynamism of the Mother Earth.

00:10:29.260 --> 00:10:37.880
“We must have this, we must have that, we
must get this, we must enjoy this,” All

00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:38.980
right.

00:10:38.980 --> 00:10:40.160
But what is the ultimate?

00:10:40.160 --> 00:10:46.630
I mean how much we have been able to absorb
it and what have we – giving others, what

00:10:46.630 --> 00:10:48.170
is our fruit of this tree that we are?

00:10:48.170 --> 00:10:55.640
The reason is, we have lacked wisdom.

00:10:55.640 --> 00:10:56.850
He was wisdom.

00:10:56.850 --> 00:11:02.930
He is the One who emits wisdom, who balances
our ego, superego, everything.

00:11:02.930 --> 00:11:06.630
You know where He stands, that Deity.

00:11:06.630 --> 00:11:13.190
But the people who followed Him, or who called
themselves Christians, where is the wisdom

00:11:13.190 --> 00:11:14.360
gone?

00:11:14.360 --> 00:11:20.880
Wisdom is one thing lacking in all of them.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:24.360
What is the reason?

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:29.640
Because we just thought that He was crucified
because He was a poor Man?

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:32.410
Or I don’t know what we thought of Him.

00:11:32.410 --> 00:11:36.690
I can’t understand human beings, what is
the lesson we have taken from His life?

00:11:36.690 --> 00:11:41.210
And the Christian nations have advanced so
much materially.

00:11:41.210 --> 00:11:43.200
Can you imagine?

00:11:43.200 --> 00:11:52.210
They do not know that poverty is such a blissful
thing sometimes.

00:11:52.210 --> 00:11:55.230
And then now a reaction has started.

00:11:55.230 --> 00:11:59.360
I’m sure reaction will also take you to
another extreme, you’ll miss the point.

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:04.070
It’s like a madman running to one end and
when he goes from there he runs to another

00:12:04.070 --> 00:12:05.070
end.

00:12:05.070 --> 00:12:06.620
Have you ever seen a wild boar running?

00:12:06.620 --> 00:12:09.130
Have you ever seen a wild boar running?

00:12:09.130 --> 00:12:15.340
You see, it’s very easy to get out of the
way of a wild boar because he just runs straightforward,

00:12:15.340 --> 00:12:17.500
till he meets some opposition.

00:12:17.500 --> 00:12:18.500
Straightforward.

00:12:18.500 --> 00:12:19.500
He wouldn’t see this side, that side.

00:12:19.500 --> 00:12:22.570
If you can just keep away from the line from
where he’s moving he will not hit you.

00:12:22.570 --> 00:12:25.580
Then again he comes back in the same way.

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:28.330
Goes this way, comes back.

00:12:28.330 --> 00:12:32.040
[Laughter]That is our movement has been about
ourselves.

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:37.830
What have we done out of our life?

00:12:37.830 --> 00:12:39.450
Let’s see.

00:12:39.450 --> 00:12:47.130
While we are capable, we are the seeds which
are going to render the real fruits.

00:12:47.130 --> 00:12:52.380
We are capable, you know now that.

00:12:52.380 --> 00:12:57.270
And that is why first of all we have done
the greatest harm to ourselves by ruining

00:12:57.270 --> 00:12:59.250
all our sustenance within ourselves.

00:12:59.250 --> 00:13:06.450
As I told you the other day in the lecture,
that how we have to maintain our sustenance.

00:13:06.450 --> 00:13:17.350
I hope it was not too much for you to – if
you feel that I was trying to tell the people

00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:23.390
also they say, a group of people who think
this is all conditioning.

00:13:23.390 --> 00:13:31.370
Actually, we are so confused in modern times
about everything.

00:13:31.370 --> 00:13:39.250
Supposing a plane has to take off, all its
parts are to be in a proper proportion, are

00:13:39.250 --> 00:13:44.790
to be tied together to the main body.

00:13:44.790 --> 00:13:48.030
Otherwise everything will go helter-skelter,
isn’t it?

00:13:48.030 --> 00:13:58.430
Now if you have to jump into your unconscious,
all your parts of the being should be attached

00:13:58.430 --> 00:14:08.650
to the gravity of the body, to your sustenance,
otherwise you’ll go helter-skelter.

00:14:08.650 --> 00:14:15.790
Will you say that a – putting the plane
in that way is conditioning it, for its freedom?

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:22.720
You have much more freedom when it is properly
done.

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:28.700
A person who is properly prepared for this
flight, has much more freedom than people

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:32.710
who think that one nose is lying this, and
ears are lying on the other side, then eyes

00:14:32.710 --> 00:14:35.950
are going on the other side, his mind is going
on the third side, his stomach is going on

00:14:35.950 --> 00:14:36.950
the other side.

00:14:36.950 --> 00:14:37.950
[Laughter]

00:14:37.950 --> 00:14:43.420
Here he is listening to Me and he’s thinking
of his food.

00:14:43.420 --> 00:14:48.070
His eyes are looking at something else.

00:14:48.070 --> 00:14:50.720
His feet are moving.

00:14:50.720 --> 00:14:52.050
He’s jumpy.

00:14:52.050 --> 00:14:54.710
There’s no proper binding.

00:14:54.710 --> 00:15:08.840
And that’s why the conditioning has a word
in Sanskrit language as samskara.

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:09.930
Samskar.

00:15:09.930 --> 00:15:20.810
Now “sam” means “good, beautiful,”
or you can say “which are good to your Spirit."

00:15:20.810 --> 00:15:29.040
Even to add to that they can say “susamskara,”
means “good conditionings,” where you

00:15:29.040 --> 00:15:31.810
are to be chiselled out.

00:15:31.810 --> 00:15:48.180
And in that chiselling, if you understand
it is for not only your good, but for your

00:15:48.180 --> 00:15:49.180
flight, then you do not give everything to
the winds.

00:15:49.180 --> 00:15:58.980
And this is the biggest mistake we have committed,
when we started on the flight of our freedom.

00:15:58.980 --> 00:16:02.910
How can you have your freedom when you are
bound by everything?

00:16:02.910 --> 00:16:06.930
You must go to the pub in the evening.

00:16:06.930 --> 00:16:09.910
You must go for your dancing [Laughter].

00:16:09.910 --> 00:16:14.279
You must see a friend who smokes and must
smoke with him.

00:16:14.279 --> 00:16:18.790
You have to attend a party where you have
to drink.

00:16:18.790 --> 00:16:21.370
You must sleep at some particular time.

00:16:21.370 --> 00:16:24.510
Because you cannot sleep, so you must take
pills.

00:16:24.510 --> 00:16:32.560
You have to have girlfriends or boyfriends,
spend money on their – I don’t know what

00:16:32.560 --> 00:16:34.980
you call – dates, and things like that.

00:16:34.980 --> 00:16:39.900
I mean, how frivolous the whole thing sounds
to Me.

00:16:39.900 --> 00:16:41.230
Same thing in India.

00:16:41.230 --> 00:16:50.890
I mean they have other frivolities.

00:16:50.890 --> 00:16:56.110
But when you understand through your Self
Realization your self-esteem, then you try

00:16:56.110 --> 00:17:01.100
to think: “Then what have I done of my life?”

00:17:01.100 --> 00:17:07.170
You are like diamonds thrown into dust.

00:17:07.170 --> 00:17:12.190
You must find out your relative relationship
with all these useless things where the money

00:17:12.190 --> 00:17:20.670
is wasted, you are frittered away, your time
is wasted, everything wasted, just find out.

00:17:20.670 --> 00:17:26.670
Once you discover that, then you start detaching
yourself from that.

00:17:26.670 --> 00:17:31.419
But first and foremost thing I’m sorry to
say – it is may call conditioning or anything

00:17:31.419 --> 00:17:43.740
– are these important things are, ten things
I told you the other time.

00:17:43.740 --> 00:17:51.480
Now all the gurus, all the gurus who came,
say from we can start from Socrates, then

00:17:51.480 --> 00:18:01.910
Abraham, Moses – this is the Guru Tattwa,
is the principle of master, primordial masters.

00:18:01.910 --> 00:18:06.730
The principle is born again and again.

00:18:06.730 --> 00:18:13.150
In India we can say the Adi Nath, we had one
Adi Nath, the Guru long time back.

00:18:13.150 --> 00:18:25.180
Then we had Dattatreya, we had Janaka, Nanaka,
Sai Nath.

00:18:25.180 --> 00:18:39.140
We had in the Middle East Mohammed Sahib,
Lao Tse in China, Confucius – all these

00:18:39.140 --> 00:18:53.160
great Principles of Gurus who were born, they
had one job to do is to establish your dharma.

00:18:53.160 --> 00:18:58.530
Their job was not to give you Realization,
you must understand, everyone has one’s

00:18:58.530 --> 00:18:59.530
own job.

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:04.050
See Mine is a horrible job [She laughs] because
I have to do everybody’s jobs.

00:19:04.050 --> 00:19:06.920
But Their job was just to establish your dharma.

00:19:06.920 --> 00:19:13.530
They came at that time, in those places where
it was needed the most.

00:19:13.530 --> 00:19:17.170
So these ten principles as I told you, They
established.

00:19:17.170 --> 00:19:23.690
They are created in the Void, as you see here
the Void part, this part is made out of the

00:19:23.690 --> 00:19:25.530
water element.

00:19:25.530 --> 00:19:34.890
So whatever miracles They did, had something
to do with water, like They could create water

00:19:34.890 --> 00:19:36.530
anywhere they wanted to.

00:19:36.530 --> 00:19:40.730
They would not cure people.

00:19:40.730 --> 00:19:51.870
All of Them have created water in the desert
or in the places where …like in … Nanaka

00:19:51.870 --> 00:19:59.040
has created a Panja Sahab they call it, everywhere
They have been able to create water.

00:19:59.040 --> 00:20:02.190
Whatever They touched, They could create water
out of it.

00:20:02.190 --> 00:20:14.070
Water is the life, life force which sustains
us; without water we cannot live, that is

00:20:14.070 --> 00:20:15.450
the sustenance.

00:20:15.450 --> 00:20:27.040
But, They actually are symbolized in an ocean,
in the ocean, because They give us the salt,

00:20:27.040 --> 00:20:29.950
the salt of life, which gives us the sustenance.

00:20:29.950 --> 00:20:34.860
If you see the salt, if we do not have salt
in our body, we’ll have no sustenance.

00:20:34.860 --> 00:20:41.880
Christ has said, “You are the salt."

00:20:41.880 --> 00:20:43.202
Who are these “you”?

00:20:43.202 --> 00:20:47.790
Are the people whom I was facing yesterday
and today.

00:20:47.790 --> 00:20:52.750
You are the gurus of today.

00:20:52.750 --> 00:20:55.990
But see with how many powers you have come.

00:20:55.990 --> 00:20:56.990
Just think of it.

00:20:56.990 --> 00:20:59.380
These Gurus did not have to give Realization.

00:20:59.380 --> 00:21:03.780
You can raise the Kundalini, you can give
Realization, you can cure people.

00:21:03.780 --> 00:21:08.570
Today Djamel asked Me that: “Mother did
They have the powers to cure?”

