00:39:03.720 --> 00:39:08.580
holiday drink, fight with wife, come back
and have a divorce.

00:39:08.580 --> 00:39:15.450
Always after a holiday, the after-effects
of the alcohol you can see very clearly.

00:39:15.450 --> 00:39:21.410
In India, thank God we do not go out for holidays
at all, we don’t believe in holidaying,

00:39:21.410 --> 00:39:23.320
at all!

00:39:23.320 --> 00:39:29.100
At the most if you have to go somewhere, we
go to some festival or to somebody’s marriage

00:39:29.100 --> 00:39:35.010
or something; if there is an occasion only
then we move out of the houses, we are gruhasthas,

00:39:35.010 --> 00:39:39.900
we settle in the family, gruhasthas who stays
in the gruha, householders.

00:39:39.900 --> 00:39:43.520
We are not like vagabond gypsies all the time
moving about.

00:39:43.520 --> 00:39:48.050
It’s all right once in a while, just to
enjoy a picnic or something.

00:39:48.050 --> 00:39:50.410
I mean you are not scouts all your life.

00:39:50.410 --> 00:39:53.910
Yes, it’s so maddening, you don’t know.

00:39:53.910 --> 00:39:59.020
My husband’s office there are two great
executives, British, they cycle down to the

00:39:59.020 --> 00:40:00.020
office.

00:40:00.020 --> 00:40:03.250
It looks so odd, you know, with half-pants
[laughter].

00:40:03.250 --> 00:40:08.970
With such a big office, how will it look,
two half-pant people coming down, with a half-pant

00:40:08.970 --> 00:40:15.910
and perspiring and smelling and everything.

00:40:15.910 --> 00:40:17.920
It is absurd!

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:19.740
[Laughter]

00:40:19.740 --> 00:40:25.310
But there is something behind this all-frantic
effort, is you are seeking something.

00:40:25.310 --> 00:40:32.100
Some people think that by going to holidays
you will achieve something.

00:40:32.100 --> 00:40:36.810
I mean music, what have you achieved in music
now, I don’t understand.

00:40:36.810 --> 00:40:41.100
By going to these holidays, if you have achieved
this kind of music which shatters every part

00:40:41.100 --> 00:40:50.750
of your skin, I mean when I hear it, you know,
the whole vibrations go on, jamming into it

00:40:50.750 --> 00:40:51.750
(?).

00:40:51.750 --> 00:40:55.780
And your bad livers, think of that at least,
bad livers, your skin diseases, your skin

00:40:55.780 --> 00:40:59.650
cancers.

00:40:59.650 --> 00:41:03.740
All this in the presence of the guru, the
sea.

00:41:03.740 --> 00:41:04.910
Can you imagine?

00:41:04.910 --> 00:41:10.810
There is no auspiciousness in this, you do
not understand.

00:41:10.810 --> 00:41:14.900
The sea is to be worshipped.

00:41:14.900 --> 00:41:17.650
It’s a temple.

00:41:17.650 --> 00:41:24.020
It teaches you, it has given you such a lot.

00:41:24.020 --> 00:41:29.510
Think of the sea, what it has given you.

00:41:29.510 --> 00:41:32.210
Without the sea, what would have been your
condition?

00:41:32.210 --> 00:41:33.349
In England specially.

00:41:33.349 --> 00:41:40.250
It taught you challenge, it gave you ideas
how to go abroad, it has given you such a

00:41:40.250 --> 00:41:41.250
lot.

00:41:41.250 --> 00:41:45.400
All your wealth comes from sea and what are
you doing about your Lakshmi?

00:41:45.400 --> 00:41:51.330
And do you know, the Lakshmi Tattwa which
resides in the centre, is born out of the

00:41:51.330 --> 00:41:52.330
sea.

00:41:52.330 --> 00:41:56.730
Actually he is your grandfather.

00:41:56.730 --> 00:42:02.930
Do you have any respect for him?

00:42:02.930 --> 00:42:08.590
So much to learn, from the sea, from the guru.

00:42:08.590 --> 00:42:11.710
It never leaves its boundaries.

00:42:11.710 --> 00:42:13.290
It keeps to that.

00:42:13.290 --> 00:42:20.230
If you try to press the sea from one side
it will show on the other side, somewhere.

00:42:20.230 --> 00:42:26.250
Such a huge thing, it gets all the water from
all over the world, but it keeps its boundaries.

00:42:26.250 --> 00:42:31.880
It never crosses it, unless and until you
press it.

00:42:31.880 --> 00:42:39.990
That’s the sign of a magnanimous great personality:
it keeps its boundaries – I mean, so far

00:42:39.990 --> 00:42:48.460
and not that – The dignity of it is – I
don’t know if there’s a word like maryada

00:42:48.460 --> 00:42:55.040
in English language – is the boundaries
of decency and decorum.

00:42:55.040 --> 00:42:56.790
Then it gives you the rain.

00:42:56.790 --> 00:43:07.570
It gives you the basis of your food.

00:43:07.570 --> 00:43:08.920
Sea is the father.

00:43:08.920 --> 00:43:22.110
And where do they meet, really in the most
beautiful way, the sea and the Mother Earth?

00:43:22.110 --> 00:43:32.410
They meet at the Sahasrara on the Himalayas
where all the clouds freeze and cover completely

00:43:32.410 --> 00:43:37.619
the Mother Earth, where there is snow all
over, on the Alps.

00:43:37.619 --> 00:43:40.619
It’s complete purity.

00:43:40.619 --> 00:43:55.609
These are too subtle things for people who
are not seeking, but I’m talking to seekers.

00:43:55.609 --> 00:44:07.240
You have to be subtler people to understand
the beauty of the sea, its poetry of a guru.

00:44:07.240 --> 00:44:14.550
When it roars, you see, the roaring of the
sea challenges you: “Come up my child, come

00:44:14.550 --> 00:44:19.500
up my disciple, come up, come along."

00:44:19.500 --> 00:44:26.800
To Me sea is like a father.

00:44:26.800 --> 00:44:31.010
I’ve traveled by sea so much, so much.

00:44:31.010 --> 00:44:36.780
And anytime I have traveled it has carried
Me like a very gentle mother.

00:44:36.780 --> 00:44:40.870
Never a bad weather, such a nice weather.

00:44:40.870 --> 00:44:41.870
Always.

00:44:41.870 --> 00:44:46.320
It’s so kind, it’s so kind to Me.

00:44:46.320 --> 00:44:52.190
Once I was coming from Japan and they said,
“There are typhoons coming."

00:44:52.190 --> 00:44:54.109
Five typhoons were coming.

00:44:54.109 --> 00:44:56.640
They never touched My ship.

00:44:56.640 --> 00:44:57.640
Nowhere.

00:44:57.640 --> 00:44:59.240
People were amazed.

00:44:59.240 --> 00:45:05.320
And we were coming to Bombay from Colombo,
when we turned round it was monsoon.

00:45:05.320 --> 00:45:06.490
They said, “Now."

00:45:06.490 --> 00:45:07.640
The captain was quite amazed, you see.

00:45:07.640 --> 00:45:09.960
He said, “But now, you cannot help it.

00:45:09.960 --> 00:45:15.800
The wind will go in the other direction and
we are going to have a bad time."

00:45:15.800 --> 00:45:20.030
But what a smooth lake, just like a mirror,
beautiful!

00:45:20.030 --> 00:45:24.010
Just like a gentle mother.

00:45:24.010 --> 00:45:28.160
It carried Me on its sari I felt.

00:45:28.160 --> 00:45:33.400
So beautiful.

00:45:33.400 --> 00:45:40.320
And such a sea you insult, because you are
ignorant, because you are blind.

00:45:40.320 --> 00:45:45.300
I wish the sea forgives you, but gurus do
not forgive easily.

00:45:45.300 --> 00:45:46.480
Mother is different.

00:45:46.480 --> 00:45:52.310
Gurus are hard taskmasters, you see.

00:45:52.310 --> 00:46:00.000
They normally do not forgive you.

00:46:00.000 --> 00:46:09.180
Now you have heard about Ravi Shankar who
is a great musician who plays sitar.

00:46:09.180 --> 00:46:17.390
I know when he was studying in – he was
in the beginning a student of Allauddin Khasa.

00:46:17.390 --> 00:46:23.980
Allauddin Khasa was a Realized soul, a great
man, a genius, a genius he was.

00:46:23.980 --> 00:46:27.980
Absolutely a real guru, you should say.

00:46:27.980 --> 00:46:29.810
He never drank.

00:46:29.810 --> 00:46:39.000
And he was a Muslim but a worshipper of Kali,
you see, and all that.

00:46:39.000 --> 00:46:42.570
And he used to call Me “Ma."

00:46:42.570 --> 00:46:43.570
Mother.

00:46:43.570 --> 00:46:50.550
I was with My father who was the political
adviser to that State, Maihar [Madhya Pradesh].

00:46:50.550 --> 00:46:56.490
I mean you could see he was really so subtle
in everything!

00:46:56.490 --> 00:47:06.920
And he used to play that big drum which he
said the best is produced in Maihar, that’s

00:47:06.920 --> 00:47:13.201
why he settled down there, what we call is
the “pakhawaj” is the very big drum, you

00:47:13.201 --> 00:47:14.201
see.

00:47:14.201 --> 00:47:15.201
He used to play tremendously.

00:47:15.201 --> 00:47:18.539
He used to just go on into such echoes and
beautiful rendering.

00:47:18.539 --> 00:47:22.170
And he was a master of so many things like
sarod – his son himself is Ali Akbar Khan

00:47:22.170 --> 00:47:23.170
Sahib.

00:47:23.170 --> 00:47:24.830
His daughter Annapurna is a great singer and
all that.

00:47:24.830 --> 00:47:36.650
And I remember Allauddin, when we went there,
he used to respect My father very much and

00:47:36.650 --> 00:47:48.470
– also because My father was a great connoisseur
of music and a Realized soul himself, a great

00:47:48.470 --> 00:47:49.470
man.

00:47:49.470 --> 00:47:55.680
So, once he was going to play the pakhawaj
and Ravi Shankar was also sitting there you

00:47:55.680 --> 00:47:57.710
see, hiding his face on the sides.

00:47:57.710 --> 00:48:02.440
So when he had played his pakhawaj, My father
said: “Why don’t you also play some sitar

00:48:02.440 --> 00:48:08.290
to me, I would like to see how much you have
learned."

00:48:08.290 --> 00:48:09.560
He said: “No, no, sir, not today, not today."

00:48:09.560 --> 00:48:12.240
So then he went inside, for something – the
guru.

00:48:12.240 --> 00:48:15.060
He [Ravi] said: “See, are you going to see
here something?”

00:48:15.060 --> 00:48:16.630
He [father] said: “What?”

00:48:16.630 --> 00:48:24.530
“Big lump, you see, was here”, he said:
“He has broken my sitar on my head today

00:48:24.530 --> 00:48:30.810
because I played two notes wrongly.

00:48:30.810 --> 00:48:33.589
See sir."

00:48:33.589 --> 00:48:34.980
[Laughter]

00:48:34.980 --> 00:48:38.420
That was the thing.

00:48:38.420 --> 00:48:43.450
The gurus are very, very, strict people, they
have to be.

00:48:43.450 --> 00:48:48.510
And the way they used to treat the disciples.

00:48:48.510 --> 00:48:50.680
It’s not like this.

00:48:50.680 --> 00:49:05.290
The gurus you know are the gurus who are trying
to pamper your ego.

00:49:05.290 --> 00:49:06.290
Why?

00:49:06.290 --> 00:49:09.589
Because they want your purse.

00:49:09.589 --> 00:49:13.890
They don’t want to enlighten you.

00:49:13.890 --> 00:49:18.910
They say, “All right, what, you drink?

00:49:18.910 --> 00:49:19.910
All right, doesn’t matter.

00:49:19.910 --> 00:49:21.380
I can give you more.

00:49:21.380 --> 00:49:24.190
Whatever you want I’ll give you.

00:49:24.190 --> 00:49:27.630
Just pass the purse this side, that’s all.

00:49:27.630 --> 00:49:40.170
Why do you want to have these, metal, this…
some metal-like, metallic things like a, say

00:49:40.170 --> 00:49:42.310
a Rolls Royce?

00:49:42.310 --> 00:49:45.320
What’s the use, this metal thing?

00:49:45.320 --> 00:49:48.510
You pass it over to me.

00:49:48.510 --> 00:49:49.510
I’ll look after it.

00:49:49.510 --> 00:49:52.420
What is the need for you to have possessed
this grand palace?

00:49:52.420 --> 00:49:56.080
Pass it over to me.

00:49:56.080 --> 00:50:02.600
I’ll look after – you must give up everything
for me.

00:50:02.600 --> 00:50:04.300
I’ll enlighten you."

00:50:04.300 --> 00:50:09.160
Even if you may have palaces and anything,
the real guru will not look at your face.

00:50:09.160 --> 00:50:10.710
He never hankers after people, never.

00:50:10.710 --> 00:50:14.140
That’s the sign of a real guru: that he
doesn’t hanker after you: “Come along

00:50:14.140 --> 00:50:16.040
to me, come along to me.

00:50:16.040 --> 00:50:18.250
All right, how many people are coming?

00:50:18.250 --> 00:50:21.330
Now have an organization and run a big mission
about it."

00:50:21.330 --> 00:50:27.130
And then the people are coming and write your
names and you become the members of the society

00:50:27.130 --> 00:50:29.770
and all that.

00:50:29.770 --> 00:50:34.680
A real guru will sit in some odd place, where
you have to go seven miles up, walking, falling,

00:50:34.680 --> 00:50:36.530
somewhere hidden, and there you go and you
find he’s not there.

00:50:36.530 --> 00:50:37.530
[Laughter]You break your legs on the way.

00:50:37.530 --> 00:50:39.190
[Shri Mataji laughs, laughter]

00:50:39.190 --> 00:50:41.300
But they know so many things.

00:50:41.300 --> 00:50:45.950
According to them, you are not to be treated
that kindly.

00:50:45.950 --> 00:50:50.040
And they tell Me that “Mother, what is Your
whim?”.

00:50:50.040 --> 00:50:51.950
And “We can’t understand.

00:50:51.950 --> 00:50:56.339
For us, we had to work so hard to get these
vibrations."

00:50:56.339 --> 00:51:02.359
One gentleman has told that: “I was a frog.

00:51:02.359 --> 00:51:05.710
Since then I’ve been seeking.

00:51:05.710 --> 00:51:11.350
And I’ve spent how many years I don’t
know, so many thousand years to get vibrations,

00:51:11.350 --> 00:51:16.480
while Mother has just given you like this!

00:51:16.480 --> 00:51:18.890
What is your speciality?

00:51:18.890 --> 00:51:21.580
Are you going to give your life for Mother?”

00:51:21.580 --> 00:51:23.260
And all sort of questions.

00:51:23.260 --> 00:51:24.260
[She laughs]

00:51:24.260 --> 00:51:26.960
So I asked him: “Why did you tell them?

00:51:26.960 --> 00:51:28.640
I don’t want their life.

00:51:28.640 --> 00:51:30.660
What’s the use of their life?

00:51:30.660 --> 00:51:32.839
I want their Spirit."

00:51:32.839 --> 00:51:36.480
He said, “But why these?”

00:51:36.480 --> 00:51:40.119
I said, “Are you jealous?”

00:51:40.119 --> 00:51:41.119
[Laughter]

00:51:41.119 --> 00:51:45.410
They say that “Mother, You carry on with
them.

00:51:45.410 --> 00:51:48.110
We can’t face this, human beings are horrible."

00:51:48.110 --> 00:51:59.820
And I’ve told you that I asked one person
to go to America, he ran away, within two

00:51:59.820 --> 00:52:00.820
days.

00:52:00.820 --> 00:52:01.820
Within two days.

00:52:01.820 --> 00:52:05.720
He would not face Americans – the real ones.

00:52:05.720 --> 00:52:09.440
The unreal ones are very nice, you see.

00:52:09.440 --> 00:52:11.920
There’s mutual understanding going on.

00:52:11.920 --> 00:52:13.600
So these hard taskmasters are so beautiful.

00:52:13.600 --> 00:52:15.220
From outside they look so harsh.

00:52:15.220 --> 00:52:17.070
Inside, they are so beautiful.

00:52:17.070 --> 00:52:20.330
You must know how to please them.

00:52:20.330 --> 00:52:24.710
For example, I went to see one guru once and
all the boys were against it.

00:52:24.710 --> 00:52:30.560
He said, “Mother, we don’t believe in
any guru, why are you going to see?”

00:52:30.560 --> 00:52:35.400
I said, “I don’t believe in any guru,
who told you?

00:52:35.400 --> 00:52:36.630
I believe in all the gurus.

00:52:36.630 --> 00:52:38.470
I don’t believe in the agurus."

00:52:38.470 --> 00:52:41.800
I said, “You see the vibrations."

00:52:41.800 --> 00:52:45.950
We had to climb up and this and that, and
we went down there.

00:52:45.950 --> 00:52:49.030
And it was raining heavily, very heavily.

00:52:49.030 --> 00:52:53.660
And the guru was very angry he was sitting
there, because he could control water, I told

00:52:53.660 --> 00:52:54.660
you.

00:52:54.660 --> 00:52:56.690
He could control rain, you know.

00:52:56.690 --> 00:53:01.160
So when I went up he was doing like this,
very angry.

00:53:01.160 --> 00:53:03.390
He wouldn’t even look at Me.

00:53:03.390 --> 00:53:08.290
I went and sat down, all drenched in water
with that rain.

00:53:08.290 --> 00:53:25.070
He said, “Why did You not allow me to stop
the rain, is it because of my ego that You

00:53:25.070 --> 00:53:27.180
wanted to punish me?

00:53:27.180 --> 00:53:33.600
I didn’t want You to get drenched when You
are coming to see me."

00:53:33.600 --> 00:53:34.690
What a great thing.

00:53:34.690 --> 00:53:39.550
I mean he talked to Me as if he knew Me, you
see, the way he talked.

00:53:39.550 --> 00:53:45.020
He said, “Not even my gurus and gurus never
had such an opportunity that You are coming

00:53:45.020 --> 00:53:52.020
to see me, and I was just prepared here, and
here You are coming all drenched.

00:53:52.020 --> 00:53:56.150
What a shame for me I could not control this
rain.

00:53:56.150 --> 00:53:59.349
It’s all Your doing Mother, why did You
do it?”

00:53:59.349 --> 00:54:03.920
I said, “Should I tell you why I did it?”

00:54:03.920 --> 00:54:05.290
He said, “Why?”

00:54:05.290 --> 00:54:12.650
I said, “You see, you have bought a sari
for Me, isn’t it?

00:54:12.650 --> 00:54:20.890
And I would not take a sari from a sanyasi;
but if I get drenched, then I’ll have to

00:54:20.890 --> 00:54:21.890
take."

00:54:21.890 --> 00:54:22.890
[Laughter]

00:54:22.890 --> 00:54:23.890
The whole thing melted away.

00:54:23.890 --> 00:54:26.530
The whole thing, the whole temper, everything
melted away.

00:54:26.530 --> 00:54:29.520
It was so sweet, you know, so sweet.

00:54:29.520 --> 00:54:35.410
There was an artist with Me, who has done
the painting.

00:54:35.410 --> 00:54:37.690
So beautiful, showing the love, you see.

00:54:37.690 --> 00:54:38.690
He just fell at My Feet.

00:54:38.690 --> 00:54:39.690
He said, “Mother, people have praised You.

00:54:39.690 --> 00:54:41.800
What words should I use to praise You?”

00:54:41.800 --> 00:54:43.020
I said, “Nothing.

00:54:43.020 --> 00:54:49.220
Your sari, you bring it for Me.

00:54:49.220 --> 00:54:52.350
First of all, I must wear your sari, I’m
all drenched."

00:54:52.350 --> 00:54:53.350
So happy.

00:54:53.350 --> 00:54:56.740
It’s so beautiful the whole thing.

00:54:56.740 --> 00:55:00.940
This is what it is.

00:55:00.940 --> 00:55:02.800
You all have to be the gurus.

00:55:02.800 --> 00:55:08.310
I know, first thing you learn is to be very,
great hard taskmasters, to begin with.

00:55:08.310 --> 00:55:10.900
That you should not do.

00:55:10.900 --> 00:55:15.490
You have to be hard taskmaster with yourself.

00:55:15.490 --> 00:55:18.750
And then, as your Mother, Who is your Guru,
is very sweet and tolerant, very kind, extremely

00:55:18.750 --> 00:55:19.750
patient.

00:55:19.750 --> 00:55:22.440
You have to deal with people like that.

00:55:22.440 --> 00:55:30.510
Because we are not dealing with people who
are seekers of that quality, who will do anything

00:55:30.510 --> 00:55:31.510
to get to God.

00:55:31.510 --> 00:55:32.849
We are dealing with people who are confused,
absolutely confused.

00:55:32.849 --> 00:55:34.230
They are saints, but they are confused.

00:55:34.230 --> 00:55:37.010
See, people come to our program, disappear.

00:55:37.010 --> 00:55:39.901
They’ll get their Realization and disappear.

00:55:39.901 --> 00:55:40.901
Then you have to give them bandhans, this
thing.

00:55:40.901 --> 00:55:41.901
You see, they are still confused.

00:55:41.901 --> 00:55:44.690
And there are so many gurus who are acting,
there are so many things that are happening,

00:55:44.690 --> 00:55:46.630
so we cannot be aggressive with them.

00:55:46.630 --> 00:55:53.460
We have to be very patient, and we have to
think about our past, how we came to Mother,

00:55:53.460 --> 00:55:57.860
how She had to convince us, how much we argued
with Her, what all we did.

00:55:57.860 --> 00:56:05.040
So these people are coming, let us try to
be kind to them and talk to them, and tell

00:56:05.040 --> 00:56:08.290
in a way which is congenial, which is beautiful.

00:56:08.290 --> 00:56:15.750
Not like those gurus because they had only
one guru, and one disciple, do you know that?

00:56:15.750 --> 00:56:20.720
The relationship was only one plus one.

00:56:20.720 --> 00:56:23.970
And that one also used to come down, many-a-times.

00:56:23.970 --> 00:56:29.109
Like one person I know, whom I met, he’s
told Me, “I have only one disciple and I’ve

00:56:29.109 --> 00:56:30.109
given him up.

00:56:30.109 --> 00:56:31.520
He’s thrown in the sea, he’s useless."

00:56:31.520 --> 00:56:32.520
I said, “What happened?”

00:56:32.520 --> 00:56:36.190
He said, “I trained him up for twenty-five
years and he’s a good-for-nothing fellow.

00:56:36.190 --> 00:56:39.110
Now he’s having a nice time, earning money.

00:56:39.110 --> 00:56:41.070
He’s a Realized soul, just imagine.

00:56:41.070 --> 00:56:45.030
And he’s having a nice time and he’s making
money out of it.

00:56:45.030 --> 00:56:49.450
This is the last story I’ll tell you."

00:56:49.450 --> 00:56:51.849
I said, “All right, where is he?”

00:56:51.849 --> 00:56:54.480
He told Me his name, this Maharaj.

00:56:54.480 --> 00:56:58.030
I said, “All right, I’ll see him, don’t
you worry."

00:56:58.030 --> 00:57:03.590
And when this fellow came in Bombay, one lady
telephoned to Me, “Mother, you wanted to

00:57:03.590 --> 00:57:06.940
meet this Maharaji, he’s coming to my house."

00:57:06.940 --> 00:57:09.910
I said, “All right, tell him I’m coming
to see him."

00:57:09.910 --> 00:57:15.420
I went down to see him, he was smoking cigarettes
like this, sitting like this.

00:57:15.420 --> 00:57:18.730
“Oh Mataji has come, very nice” and all
that.

00:57:18.730 --> 00:57:22.490
He, of course, I mean he touched My feet like
this, “All right, sit down."

00:57:22.490 --> 00:57:26.600
And there were ladies pressing his feet and
all that and he was talking to them very…

00:57:26.600 --> 00:57:31.420
trying to show lot of arrogance in My presence.

00:57:31.420 --> 00:57:34.640
I was just looking at him.

00:57:34.640 --> 00:57:36.780
Then he said, “Oh.

00:57:36.780 --> 00:57:40.970
So, my guru comes to see You in Bombay.

00:57:40.970 --> 00:57:43.630
Why is he leaving his place?

00:57:43.630 --> 00:57:45.849
Why should he do this?”.

00:57:45.849 --> 00:57:50.730
And all sorts of thing he was talking, against
his guru.

00:57:50.730 --> 00:57:57.200
I said, “All right, now I’m going, but
I will put some sindoor on your head, just

00:57:57.200 --> 00:58:02.330
to put a tilak on your head,” I said.

00:58:02.330 --> 00:58:09.260
So I took some sindoor, put it on his head;
Agnya Chakra I moved it.

00:58:09.260 --> 00:58:10.920
Then I said, “Now you put."

00:58:10.920 --> 00:58:11.920
When he start put…

00:58:11.920 --> 00:58:14.730
I sucked his hand, you see completely, and
he started, “Ahee-hee-hee-hee-hee he-he-he-he-he-he-he-he-he-he."

00:58:14.730 --> 00:58:17.020
He said, “Mother, Mother what are You doing,
what are You doing?”

00:58:17.020 --> 00:58:18.760
I said, “What am I doing?

00:58:18.760 --> 00:58:24.760
Will you please take back all the words you
have said about your guru?

00:58:24.760 --> 00:58:26.119
You have no shame.

00:58:26.119 --> 00:58:31.740
Twenty-five years that man worked on you and
you’re bringing all the shame here.

00:58:31.740 --> 00:58:33.670
Will you remove your hand?”

00:58:33.670 --> 00:58:36.740
He said, “I can’t, I can’t, I can’t!

00:58:36.740 --> 00:58:37.740
What are You doing to me?”

00:58:37.740 --> 00:58:43.260
I said, “Unless and until you promise that
you will not say a word against your guru

00:58:43.260 --> 00:58:49.000
and hold your ears, with the another hand,
or with your legs [She laughs], then only

00:58:49.000 --> 00:58:50.000
I’ll leave you."

00:58:50.000 --> 00:58:52.890
(Laughter) He said, “I’m sorry, I’m
sorry, You will drop…?”

00:58:52.890 --> 00:58:58.920
Now the others didn’t see all this conversation,
you see, they just saw his shaking, you see.

00:58:58.920 --> 00:59:02.180
When I went away he said, “See, how powerful
I am?

00:59:02.180 --> 00:59:03.180
See."

00:59:03.180 --> 00:59:06.780
[Laughter] Fools as they were, they never
realized that he was shaking, and what shaking

00:59:06.780 --> 00:59:07.780
means, you see?

00:59:07.780 --> 00:59:11.910
And he made such a fool out of them.

00:59:11.910 --> 00:59:21.650
He took from everyone, one and a quarter tola
[ed: tola is an old Indian weight equal to

00:59:21.650 --> 00:59:24.570
180 grains, 0.375 troy ounces.]

00:59:24.570 --> 00:59:32.940
gold, you see, as a dakshina, guru dakshina,
and said that “See, even Mataji – I was

00:59:32.940 --> 00:59:38.630
getting all Her powers into me, sucking all
Her Powers into me."

00:59:38.630 --> 00:59:44.910
[Laughter] And these fools believed him, you
see.

00:59:44.910 --> 00:59:54.070
And then one of them met Me at the airport
and she told Me that “He’s taken away

00:59:54.070 --> 00:59:55.320
so much money from us.

00:59:55.320 --> 01:00:02.380
That day only he made us pay for one and a
quarter tola gold for the guru dakshina."

01:00:02.380 --> 01:00:06.630
I said, “All right, I’ll see him one day,
again."

01:00:06.630 --> 01:00:09.270
But all of them were doomed like that.

01:00:09.270 --> 01:00:11.230
So, this is what it is.

01:00:11.230 --> 01:00:13.760
And he’s so attractive to people, you know.

01:00:13.760 --> 01:00:21.590
And then he was sitting on a very big thing
and the thousands are approaching him, there.

01:00:21.590 --> 01:00:25.140
But then I did some arrangements.

01:00:25.140 --> 01:00:32.380
Now he’s all right, in the jail, direct
[laughter].

01:00:32.380 --> 01:00:34.870
In the jail, direct.

01:00:34.870 --> 01:00:36.290
That’s what it is.

01:00:36.290 --> 01:00:38.640
But we had one Sahaj Yogini like this.

01:00:38.640 --> 01:00:50.670
She got her Realization and I told her, “Your
guru was no good and you don’t take anything

01:00:50.670 --> 01:01:11.020
from him, because he’ll try to give you
some siddhis and you will try to impress people."

01:01:11.020 --> 01:01:27.030
She said, “No, no Mother, I want the parama,
I want the last, the absolute, I don’t want

01:01:27.030 --> 01:01:28.210
all that."

01:01:28.210 --> 01:01:38.280
Because her guru used to carry some snakes
around and do all kinds of tricks you see,

01:01:38.280 --> 01:01:40.060
go into tantrums.

01:01:40.060 --> 01:01:47.200
When I went to America, I heard about her,
that she’s having three thousand disciples;

01:01:47.200 --> 01:01:50.940
I never had them in Bombay that time.

01:01:50.940 --> 01:01:57.099
I used to hardly get about two hundred people
somehow or other sticking on to this… thing.

01:01:57.099 --> 01:01:59.950
I said, “Three thousand.

01:01:59.950 --> 01:02:02.800
What is she doing?”

01:02:02.800 --> 01:02:19.630
I got really worried you know; I put her into
bandhan and everything.

01:02:19.630 --> 01:02:33.980
But when I came back, you won’t believe,
she had silver water carriers you see, these

01:02:33.980 --> 01:02:40.400
pitchers, she brought to wash My Feet and
this.

01:02:40.400 --> 01:02:44.690
I was so embarrassed, so embarrassed.

01:02:44.690 --> 01:02:51.819
And she showed Me, “See Mother, what work
I’m doing."

01:02:51.819 --> 01:03:00.020
Such a big photograph of Mine there, put,
and all the bhoots around.

01:03:00.020 --> 01:03:03.200
I could see all them hovering, you see, all
of them.

01:03:03.200 --> 01:03:04.200
[Laughter]

01:03:04.200 --> 01:03:05.200
I said, “What is she doing?

01:03:05.200 --> 01:03:11.060
What work has she been doing and what is she
up to?

01:03:11.060 --> 01:03:19.329
Because she’s completely gone darkened and
haunted."

01:03:19.329 --> 01:03:24.320
I asked her, “What are you doing with these
people?”

01:03:24.320 --> 01:03:26.060
“Oh Mother, you don’t know.

01:03:26.060 --> 01:03:28.030
I’ve spread Your name there.

01:03:28.030 --> 01:03:35.810
I can even tell people if they have lost their
property somewhere, wherever is the hidden

01:03:35.810 --> 01:03:38.550
money, or I tell so many things….

01:03:38.550 --> 01:03:43.810
I can even tell the name of the horse which
is going to come first."

01:03:43.810 --> 01:03:45.430
[Laughter] I said, “Very nice.

01:03:45.430 --> 01:03:49.650
What a nice Sahaj Yoga is going on here,”
you see?

01:03:49.650 --> 01:03:54.920
So I told her, “All right, you come and
see Me tomorrow at home."

01:03:54.920 --> 01:03:56.010
She came down.

01:03:56.010 --> 01:04:00.360
I had two-three people sitting, I said, “All
right, tell about them."

01:04:00.360 --> 01:04:02.900
She said, “You live near a bridge."

01:04:02.900 --> 01:04:05.870
He said, “No, never, I live near a sea.

01:04:05.870 --> 01:04:08.100
How can you bridge a sea?”

01:04:08.100 --> 01:04:09.960
Then she said this, that.

01:04:09.960 --> 01:04:11.440
He said, “No, nothing."

01:04:11.440 --> 01:04:13.300
Then she told another lady.

01:04:13.300 --> 01:04:14.410
She said, “Nothing."

01:04:14.410 --> 01:04:17.390
Third person said, “Nothing, this is not
true.

01:04:17.390 --> 01:04:21.710
You are just telling something that is not
true."

01:04:21.710 --> 01:04:26.050
So she rushed to Me, “Mother, have You taken
away all my powers?”

01:04:26.050 --> 01:04:27.050
[Laughter]

01:04:27.050 --> 01:04:30.960
I said, “If they were your powers I would
have made you sit here.

01:04:30.960 --> 01:04:32.500
These are the powers of the devil.

01:04:32.500 --> 01:04:37.620
What interest God has got to tell that ‘What
is the horse coming,’ and all that?

01:04:37.620 --> 01:04:40.180
[Laughter] Why should you tell all these things?

01:04:40.180 --> 01:04:44.460
These are not your powers, these are the powers
of the spirits which are haunting you, and

01:04:44.460 --> 01:04:48.290
which you have captured, and your guru is
doing all this job."

01:04:48.290 --> 01:04:50.050
“Oh God, I never knew."

01:04:50.050 --> 01:04:51.800
I said, “It is that.

01:04:51.800 --> 01:04:54.260
All right, say that ‘I give up.

01:04:54.260 --> 01:04:55.310
I give up.’

01:04:55.310 --> 01:04:56.360
Say it thrice."

01:04:56.360 --> 01:04:58.820
She said, “All right, I’ll say, Mother.

01:04:58.820 --> 01:05:01.620
I want the parama, I want the absolute”.

01:05:01.620 --> 01:05:07.750
She went home, but you know this popularity,
this cheap popularity, is a very enticing

01:05:07.750 --> 01:05:08.750
thing.

01:05:08.750 --> 01:05:12.870
She again carried on, and now she is in the
lunatic asylum.

01:05:12.870 --> 01:05:14.520
This is what it is.

01:05:14.520 --> 01:05:17.580
Because these spirits which help you, come
back on you and torture you.

01:05:17.580 --> 01:05:22.390
So all those people who try to deviate, even
after Realization, are corrected by the principle

01:05:22.390 --> 01:05:23.910
of guru only.

01:05:23.910 --> 01:05:27.430
With the principle of Agnya, you give Realization,
enlightenment.

01:05:27.430 --> 01:05:32.090
With the principle of Sahasrara you give integration,
but with the principle of guru you give them

01:05:32.090 --> 01:05:33.090
dharma.

01:05:33.090 --> 01:05:42.329
That’s why so many people, all of you who
came to Me, have very easily given up all

01:05:42.329 --> 01:05:46.940
these habits, because you have found the Spirit,
the joy.

01:05:46.940 --> 01:05:50.340
And then you don’t want all that.

01:05:50.340 --> 01:06:00.750
I don’t have to tell you that you have to
give up, you just give up, you just forget

01:06:00.750 --> 01:06:05.220
it, because your attention is now attached
to your Spirit.

01:06:05.220 --> 01:06:15.640
That is the job of a guru.

01:06:15.640 --> 01:06:22.200
It is said that: “Guru is that which makes
you meet the Sahib."

01:06:22.200 --> 01:06:26.630
Means: “makes you meet the Lord."

01:06:26.630 --> 01:06:27.819
He’s the guru.

01:06:27.819 --> 01:06:29.260
Otherwise all these are not gurus.

01:06:29.260 --> 01:06:32.830
But the one who has not even settled your
dharmas, who does not have his own dharmas,

01:06:32.830 --> 01:06:36.650
how can you accept them as gurus?

01:06:36.650 --> 01:06:38.520
May God bless you all.

01:06:38.520 --> 01:06:40.069
[Start of 3: informal talk to seekers]

01:06:40.069 --> 01:06:43.220
Shri Mataji [about a young child]: This is
a born Realized child.

01:06:43.220 --> 01:06:44.920
[Shri Mataji laughs]

01:06:44.920 --> 01:06:47.180
Hello, how are you?

01:06:47.180 --> 01:06:50.010
Hum, what are they catching?

01:06:50.010 --> 01:06:51.590
He is showing from his feet.

01:06:51.590 --> 01:06:53.100
All over right side Sahasrara.

01:06:53.100 --> 01:06:54.600
Right side Sahasrara means what?

01:06:54.600 --> 01:06:55.600
Superego.

01:06:55.600 --> 01:06:57.480
It comes to the right [of the brain].

01:06:57.480 --> 01:07:02.640
All feeling the heaviness on the right side,
the little child is showing.

01:07:02.640 --> 01:07:06.640
They are working, they are busy all the time.

01:07:06.640 --> 01:07:10.819
All the time they are busy.

01:07:10.819 --> 01:07:16.260
Gavin’s child’s such a little thing…
all the time.

01:07:16.260 --> 01:07:23.800
[Laughter, She laughs] Trying to clear you
out – great people they are.

01:07:23.800 --> 01:07:29.940
All the time they are working.

01:07:29.940 --> 01:07:37.800
That’s why I want you all to get married
soon, with so many great children are to be

01:07:37.800 --> 01:07:38.800
born to you.

01:07:38.800 --> 01:07:42.300
All right, I can make it cool for you, it’s
all right, don’t you worry.

01:07:42.300 --> 01:07:43.300
[Laughter]

01:07:43.300 --> 01:07:46.190
You have to think of the Moon who is your
maternal uncle.

01:07:46.190 --> 01:07:47.190
He was born with Lakshmi.

01:07:47.190 --> 01:07:49.190
There are fourteen things that were born from
the sea.

01:07:49.190 --> 01:07:52.589
One of them is also a hunter.

01:07:52.589 --> 01:07:57.140
The stick Gregoire gave Me yesterday was also,
came out of the sea.

01:07:57.140 --> 01:07:58.140
That was the fourteenth thing.

01:07:58.140 --> 01:07:59.140
Better now?

01:07:59.140 --> 01:08:00.774
Now, those who have come for the first time
should come forward, you see, it’s better

01:08:00.774 --> 01:08:01.774
in the forward line somewhere, would be better
and the second line could be – it’s all

01:08:01.774 --> 01:08:02.774
right.

01:08:02.774 --> 01:08:03.774
These people have come for the first time,
all of you?

01:08:03.774 --> 01:08:04.774
All right, can you come on these first three
lines, all right.

01:08:04.774 --> 01:08:05.774
Now who else is there?

01:08:05.774 --> 01:08:06.774
Please, come forward.

01:08:06.774 --> 01:08:11.440
As you know, Sahaja Yoga is a very subtle
thing and the main thing is it must work,

01:08:11.440 --> 01:08:20.009
it must actualize, the Kundalini must rise.

01:08:20.009 --> 01:08:31.179
You must get your Realization, that’s the
main concern is.

01:08:31.179 --> 01:08:38.150
Whatever you may say, whatever your arguments
may be or any problems may be, we are not

01:08:38.150 --> 01:08:39.150
bothered about that.

01:08:39.150 --> 01:08:43.080
What we are bothered about: that you should
meet yourself.

01:08:43.080 --> 01:08:48.900
That’s the main point we are at, and that’s
what we have to achieve.

01:08:48.900 --> 01:08:52.859
Now the problems arise out of our imbalances
in life and so many things.

01:08:52.859 --> 01:08:55.349
Whatever it is, still, the force is so great,
that you will get your Realization.

01:08:55.349 --> 01:08:56.349
Why I’m telling you?

01:08:56.349 --> 01:09:03.569
That I find people, once they get their Realization,
they think it’s done now, we are happy,

01:09:03.569 --> 01:09:05.079
then they don’t come.

01:09:05.079 --> 01:09:06.319
It’s just the germination has taken place,
the Kundalini has shot off, because She’s

01:09:06.319 --> 01:09:07.409
been waiting all these days, you see, so the
whole thing comes up as a big experience.

01:09:07.409 --> 01:09:08.409
But that doesn’t mean that you have established
it.

01:09:08.409 --> 01:09:10.869
So the second thing you have to do is to establish,
that’s very important.

01:09:10.869 --> 01:09:15.099
Much more important than getting Realization
I feel, because the Realization, if it takes

01:09:15.099 --> 01:09:18.979
place and it falls down, then what’s the
use?

01:09:18.979 --> 01:09:25.429
So you take your Realization, which you’ll
get, no doubt about it, because you all look

01:09:25.429 --> 01:09:26.429
that way.

01:09:26.429 --> 01:09:30.339
But, then you must have self-esteem and understand
that you have got it because you deserved

01:09:30.339 --> 01:09:31.339
it.

01:09:31.339 --> 01:09:34.799
Some people haven’t got it in India who
have been with Me for seven years, but you’ll

01:09:34.799 --> 01:09:35.799
get it I’m sure.

01:09:35.799 --> 01:09:36.819
That I can see clearly, you are all going
to get it.

01:09:36.819 --> 01:09:40.369
But that doesn’t mean if you get it, that
you again waste it, because this is what you

01:09:40.369 --> 01:09:41.369
have been seeking all your lives.

01:09:41.369 --> 01:09:47.139
Because in the West the problem is: though
such saints are born, they have this rambling

01:09:47.139 --> 01:09:48.259
of the brain and they start thinking.

01:09:48.259 --> 01:09:49.259
You do not get it through your rationality.

01:09:49.259 --> 01:09:50.259
You get it through your Kundalini, which you
cannot think about.

01:09:50.259 --> 01:09:52.259
So you allow it to grow, manifest itself,
and you become as good as others are.

01:09:52.259 --> 01:09:55.177
Now they are all experts and gurus, you know,
they know such a lot about Kundalini.

01:09:55.177 --> 01:09:58.120
You’ll be amazed, they are all experts,
they look just like you!

01:09:58.120 --> 01:09:59.120
They are raising Kundalini, they are giving
Realization, they know everything about it.

01:09:59.120 --> 01:10:00.120
So in the same way, you have to be.

01:10:00.120 --> 01:10:01.120
It’s a very simple thing which takes place
at any age, any time, any race, anything.

01:10:01.120 --> 01:10:02.120
The main thing is that you must have self-esteem,
you must know that you are saints.

01:10:02.120 --> 01:10:03.120
You have been saints for years and you have
been ages like this.

01:10:03.120 --> 01:10:04.120
You have been seeking and seeking and seeking.

01:10:04.120 --> 01:10:05.120
Now when you have found it, you allow it to
grow, because it’s very important, and you

01:10:05.120 --> 01:10:06.120
must know your value.

01:10:06.120 --> 01:10:07.120
That is important.

01:10:07.120 --> 01:10:08.120
Because I value you, because I see something
much deeper that you can’t see.

01:10:08.120 --> 01:10:09.120
But you don’t see that, gradually you’ll
start seeing, all right?

01:10:09.120 --> 01:10:10.120
On this promise, I’ll give you Realization.

01:10:10.120 --> 01:10:11.120
Put your hands like this.

01:10:11.120 --> 01:10:12.120
Put both the feet on the ground, straight.

01:10:12.120 --> 01:10:13.120
Sometimes I find, you see I’ve worked very
hard on people and they get lost, I feel very

01:10:13.120 --> 01:10:14.120
sorry for that.

01:10:14.120 --> 01:10:15.120
Left Swadishthana, you see [She laughs] – give
him…

01:10:15.120 --> 01:10:16.120
Like a saint he’s sitting here, great guru.

01:10:16.120 --> 01:10:17.120
[About a child]

01:10:17.120 --> 01:10:18.120
Now put your hands towards Me, like this,
and close your eyes.

01:10:18.120 --> 01:10:19.120
Please close your eyes.

01:10:19.120 --> 01:10:20.120
Now what happens is that first you become
thoughtlessly aware, nirvichar samadhi.

01:10:20.120 --> 01:10:21.120
Samadhi means enlightened awareness.

01:10:21.120 --> 01:10:22.120
You get enlightened awareness which is thoughtless.

01:10:22.120 --> 01:10:23.120
You become thoughtlessly aware.

01:10:23.120 --> 01:10:24.120
First.

01:10:24.120 --> 01:10:25.120
And in the second happening, when it crosses
the Agnya it happens to you, and when it crosses,

01:10:25.120 --> 01:10:26.120
pierces through this point called as taloo,
the fontanel bone area, you start feeling

01:10:26.120 --> 01:10:27.120
the radiation of your Spirit in your hands,
